Interview prep: scripted responses for every potential red flag question so nothing catches me off guard

Format as a red flag neutralization guide with before/after resume sections and scripted interview responses for each concern.My concerns: [DESCRIBE ANY GAPS, SHORT TENURES, LAYOFFS, OR CAREER CHANGES YOU'RE WORRIED ABOUT EXPLAINING]

